Paper: hep-th/0009222

Date: 2000-09-27

Title: Schwinger terms in two-dimensional gravitation and Kallen's method

Authors: R. A. Bertlmann and E. Kohlprath

Journal-ref: Czech.J.Phys. 51 (2001) 211-218

We evaluate the gravitational Schwinger terms for the specifictwo-dimensional model of Weyl fermions in a gravitational background fieldusing a technique introduced by Kallen and find a relation which connects theSchwinger terms with the linearized gravitational anomalies.